staypuft fields

fields.Rd

staypuft fields

fields

Format

An object of class list of length 13.

Types of fields

  • Missing

  • Character

  • UUID

  • Number

  • Integer

  • Boolean

  • Any

  • Date

  • Nested

  • Url

  • Email

  • NamedList

  • more coming soon

Usage

You can use any supported fields in the fields object.

You can call the field like fields$character(), or pass supported arguments like fields$character(data_key = "foobar")
